@startuml sd_SalaryCalculationService_calculateSingle
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title SalaryCalculationService.calculateSingle(emp, ym, items, vars) - 单个员工工资计算

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SalaryCalculationService" as CalcSvc
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as ItemRepo
participant "SocialSecurityService" as SsSvc
participant "TaxService" as TaxSvc
participant "SalaryRecordRepository" as RecRepo
participant "ObjectMapper" as OM
participant "SalaryRecord\n(实体)" as Rec

Client -> CalcSvc: calculateSingle(employee, yearMonth, items, variableValues)
note right of CalcSvc #F0F8FF
  **Step 1: 获取上月记录**
  用于累计值计算
end note
CalcSvc -> RecRepo: findByEmployeeIdAndYearMonth(empId, lastMonth)
RecRepo --> CalcSvc: Optional<SalaryRecord>
note right of CalcSvc #F0F8FF
  **Step 2: 逐项计算工资项**
  for each SalaryItem:
  - 有公式: eval公式(引用其他项code)
  - 无公式: 默认值或变量值
  - 累加EARNING→grossPay
  - 累加SOCIAL→socialInsurance
  - 累加FUND→housingFund
end note
loop 每个活动工资项
  CalcSvc -> CalcSvc: evaluateItem(item, emp, ym, vars, itemValueMap)
  note right: 公式引擎: replace(code→value) → 简单四则运算
end
note right of CalcSvc #F0F8FF
  **Step 3: 计算累计值**
  cumulativeIncome = grossPay + 上月累计
  cumulativeDeduction = 社保+公积金 + 上月累计
end note
CalcSvc -> SsSvc: calculate(employee, yearMonth)
SsSvc --> CalcSvc: {socialInsurance, housingFund}
note right of CalcSvc #F0F8FF
  **Step 4: 计算个税**
  taxable = cumulativeIncome - 5000×月数
            - cumulativeDeduction
end note
CalcSvc -> TaxSvc: calculateTax(...)
TaxSvc --> CalcSvc: incomeTax
note right of CalcSvc #F0F8FF
  **Step 5: 计算实发**
  netPay = grossPay - incomeTax
           - socialInsurance - housingFund
end note
CalcSvc -> OM: writeValueAsString(itemValueMap)
OM --> CalcSvc: JSON字符串
note right of CalcSvc #F0F8FF
  **Step 6: 构建SalaryRecord**
  含所有累计值字段
  status=DRAFT
end note
CalcSvc -> RecRepo: save(record)
RecRepo --> CalcSvc: 持久化后SalaryRecord
CalcSvc --> Client: SalaryRecord
@enduml
